  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  all patients undergoing ERCP with unintended cannulation or opifiacation of main
             pancreatic duct

          -  age &gt; 17 years

          -  signed informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  intention to intervene main pancreatic duct

          -  age &lt; 18 years

          -  pregnancy

          -  absent of signed informed consent
      </textblock>
